{"id":1881,"date":"2019-05-06T16:19:23","date_gmt":"2019-05-06T09:19:23","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/?p=1881"},"modified":"2019-05-06T16:19:23","modified_gmt":"2019-05-06T09:19:23","slug":"huong-dan-cach-hoa-giai-nha-chung-cu-khong-hop-huong","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/huong-dan-cach-hoa-giai-nha-chung-cu-khong-hop-huong","title":{"rendered":"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p h\u01b0\u1edbng"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111em l\u1ea1i cho qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m phong th\u1ee7y trong nh\u00e0 \u1edf, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0. <strong>Thietkethicongdn.com<\/strong> xin chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/huong-dan-cach-hoa-giai-nha-chung-cu-khong-hop-huong\"><em><strong>c\u00e1ch h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p h\u01b0\u1edbng<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/span>. C\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1882 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/H\u01b0\u1edbng-d\u1eabn-c\u00e1ch-h\u00f3a-gi\u1ea3i-nh\u00e0-chung-c\u01b0-kh\u00f4ng-h\u1ee3p-h\u01b0\u1edbng.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" \/><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>H\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p h\u01b0\u1edbng c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a g\u00ec?<\/strong><\/h2>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y nay, th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 v\u1eeba \u00fd v\u00e0 h\u1ee3p phong th\u1ee7y. M\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n do \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n gia ch\u1ee7, m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u00e1c h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng theo khu\u00f4n m\u1eabu. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn mua ph\u1ea3i c\u0103n nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edbng x\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p hi\u1ebfm g\u1eb7p.<\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo quan ni\u1ec7m, h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng th\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0. N\u1ebfu ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ed1t, h\u1ee3p m\u1ec7nh ch\u1ee7, s\u1ebd g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0, gi\u00fap l\u01b0u th\u00f4ng c\u00e1c lu\u1ed3ng kh\u00ed thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 gi\u00f3 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. V\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, nh\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng x\u1ea5u s\u1ebd d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u r\u1ee7i ro cho cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.<\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 x\u1ea5u l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u, ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0, ho\u1eb7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c h\u01b0\u1edbng kh\u00f4ng thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n, ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 xui r\u1ee7i, mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh an cho cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0&gt;&gt;&gt; \u0110\u1eebng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1: <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/kinh-nghiem-chon-xac-dinh-huong-nha-hop-tuoi\">Kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ecdn &#8211; x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 h\u1ee3p tu\u1ed5i<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00e1ch h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p h\u01b0\u1edbng<\/strong><\/h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>1. H\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 2 c\u1eeda ch\u00ednh xung \u0111\u1ed1i nhau<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; H\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh l\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng th\u1eb3ng g\u00f3c v\u1edbi c\u1eeda ch\u00ednh, c\u00e1c l\u1ed1i \u0111i kh\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u1ee5. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u1ebfu nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 2 c\u1eeda ch\u00ednh xung \u0111\u1ed1i nhau c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng g\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00e1t qu\u00e1i ho\u1eb7c chu\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 treo \u1edf gi\u1eefa ph\u00f2ng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1885 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/H\u01b0\u1edbng-d\u1eabn-c\u00e1ch-h\u00f3a-gi\u1ea3i-nh\u00e0-chung-c\u01b0-kh\u00f4ng-h\u1ee3p-h\u01b0\u1edbng3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"428\" \/><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2. H\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 c\u1eeda ch\u00ednh th\u00f4ng c\u1eeda h\u1eadu<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; Theo d\u00e2n gian, c\u1eeda ch\u00ednh th\u00f4ng c\u1eeda h\u1eadu s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n t\u00e0i b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t tho\u00e1t, hao t\u1ed5n. C\u00e1ch h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i l\u00e0 n\u00ean s\u1eeda l\u1ea1i c\u1eeda ho\u1eb7c ch\u1eafn gi\u1eefa 2 c\u1eeda b\u1eb1ng t\u1ea5m b\u00ecnh phong \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n th\u00f4ng nhau.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>3. H\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 s\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng giao th\u00f4ng huy\u1ebft m\u1ea1ch<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; Trong phong th\u1ee7y nh\u00e0 \u1edf, nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn giao th\u00f4ng huy\u1ebft m\u1ea1ch \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn sinh ho\u1ea1t, s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 t\u00e0i v\u1eadn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n s\u1ed1ng trong khu chung c\u01b0. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh x\u00e2y t\u00f2a chung c\u01b0 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y, th\u00ec t\u1ea7ng 1 n\u00ean thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf khu d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed, kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf, t\u1ea7ng 2 tr\u1edf l\u00ean n\u00ean x\u00e2y l\u00f9i v\u00e0o ph\u00eda sau m\u1ed9t \u00edt \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng. N\u00ean b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t trong nh\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u g\u1ed7 ho\u1eb7c c\u00e2y xanh. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng s\u00f3ng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eeb tr\u1ee5 \u0111i\u1ec7n ph\u00e1t ra l\u00e0m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1883 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/H\u01b0\u1edbng-d\u1eabn-c\u00e1ch-h\u00f3a-gi\u1ea3i-nh\u00e0-chung-c\u01b0-kh\u00f4ng-h\u1ee3p-h\u01b0\u1edbng1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"428\" \/><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>4. H\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e2m th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o nh\u00e0<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc g\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00e1t qu\u00e1i ho\u1eb7c chu\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i hung kh\u00ed. H\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y theo phong th\u1ee7y s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn gia ch\u1ee7 hao t\u00e0i, ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c &#8220;\u0110\u1ed9i n\u00f3n ra \u0111i&#8221;. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng x\u1ea5u cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u00e0 n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea1ch anh t\u00edm ho\u1eb7c th\u1ea1ch anh v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n l\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1884 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/H\u01b0\u1edbng-d\u1eabn-c\u00e1ch-h\u00f3a-gi\u1ea3i-nh\u00e0-chung-c\u01b0-kh\u00f4ng-h\u1ee3p-h\u01b0\u1edbng2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"419\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean. H\u00e3y ghi nh\u1edb c\u00e1c c\u00e1ch h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng nh\u00e9! Ch\u00fac cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n an y\u00ean v\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u may m\u1eafn.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0&gt;&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam:\u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/huong-dan-cach-xem-huong-nha-khi-mua-chung-cu\">C\u00e1ch xem h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 khi mua chung c\u01b0<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>V\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111em l\u1ea1i cho qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m phong th\u1ee7y trong nh\u00e0 \u1edf, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0. Thietkethicongdn.com xin chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p h\u01b0\u1edbng. C\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u00e9! H\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 chung&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":1882,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1881"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1881"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1881\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1886,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1881\/revisions\/1886"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1882"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1881"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1881"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1881"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}